&lt;p&gt;The Claims Manager position at Golden State Claims Adjusters reports to the Senior Vice President of Claims and supervises a team of Claims Supervisors and operational staff. The Claims Manager acts as a liaison between Golden State and our carrier partners and provides strategic and operational leadership on assigned programs to ensure regulatory compliance, operational efficiency, strong claim outcomes, and an exceptional customer experience. This role partners closely with internal stakeholders and external vendors, leverages data and reporting to identify trends and risks, and ensures Best Practices, service standards, and KPIs are consistently met.&lt;/p&gt;
