&lt;li&gt;Conduct internal audits on a quarterly basis and ensure timely remediation of findings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify, report, and track Notices of High Potential (NHP) claims and adverse trends&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Present claim files and operational results at weekly roundtables and leadership meetings&lt;/li&gt;
