&lt;p&gt;As a Corporate Accounting Supervisor with ISC, you will be responsible for overseeing the day-to-day corporate accounting functions of a growing private equity backed MGA. This role supervises the monthly close process, financial reporting, account reconciliations, and compliance with GAAP while ensuring the accuracy and integrity of the company’s financial records.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Corporate Accounting Supervisor leads and develops accounting staff, maintains strong internal controls, and drives process improvements to support scalability and growth. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
