&lt;li&gt;Assist with year-end financial audit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide supporting schedules, reconciliations, and financial information for tax filings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support acquisition accounting for mergers and acquisitions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Supervise staff accountants, including reviewing work product and provide coaching and performance feedback&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Complete special projects and financial analyses as assigned&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
