&lt;p data-start=&quot;248&quot; data-end=&quot;747&quot;&gt;Integrated Specialty Coverages (ISC) acquired Specialty Brokerage Services (SBS), a Columbus-based wholesale brokerage, in January 2026. SBS is well known for its strong personal and commercial lines capabilities, deep carrier relationships, and long-standing reputation for service excellence. This CSR will join a growing wholesale business unit, as SBS adds immediate depth to ISC’s offerings, including a niche in high-value personal lines that complements ISC’s exclusive homeowners programs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;749&quot; data-end=&quot;1082&quot;&gt;This role is responsible for delivering exceptional service, ensuring accurate processing, and maintaining efficient communication while developing a strong understanding of carrier guidelines and internal procedures. It is an excellent opportunity for someone who thrives in a fast-paced Property &amp;amp; Casualty wholesale environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1084&quot; data-end=&quot;1257&quot; data-is-last-node=&quot;&quot; data-is-only-node=&quot;&quot;&gt;Candidates considered for this role should ideally be located in the Columbus, Ohio Jacksonville, FL or Orlando, FL areas and be comfortable working remotely with occasional short-distance travel as needed.&lt;/p&gt;
