&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in Microsoft Office Suite and ability to quickly learn industry-specific software&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work collaboratively with team members and other departments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong desire to learn, explore new ideas, and seeking out new knowledge&lt;/li&gt;
